thread.title: Greg & Ann
thread.title_full: Nelson Alexander reviewed by Greg & Ann

author: Greg & Ann
title: Greg & Ann
text:
Our sale was professionally handled as were all of the staff we dealt with.
In particular we had a great relationship with Tom - he respected our needs and was never pushy in any aspect.
On the day it started to rain just as the auction was about to begin - Tom handled this well, and I think the approach added to the drama and outcome.
And the result far exceeded our expectations.
